      Welcome to GreenRoot Plant Co.! We are a company dedicated to providing the best soil for your houseplants. Our soil is made from premium ingredients and is perfect for all types of indoor plants. We believe that healthy soil makes healthy plants, and we want to help you grow the most beautiful plants possible.
    </p>
    <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      Our soil blends are carefully crafted using sustainable, peat-free materials. Peat is harmful to the environment, so we've developed alternatives that work just as well (or better!) while being better for the planet. Each blend is specifically formulated for different types of plants.
    </p>
    <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      Whether you're growing succulents, tropical plants, or anything in between, we have a soil blend that's perfect for you. All of our products are available for purchase online with fast shipping to your door.
    </p>
    
    <!-- Confusing multiple CTAs -->
