  <!-- Benefits Section - Wall of text, no visual hierarchy -->
  <section style="padding: 2rem 1rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; background: #f5f5f5;">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #333;">Why Choose Our Soil?</h2>
    
    <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      Our soil blends are made with only the highest quality ingredients. We source our materials from sustainable suppliers who share our commitment to environmental responsibility. Each ingredient is carefully selected for its specific properties and benefits to plant health.
    </p>
    
    <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      Traditional potting soil often contains peat moss, which is harvested from sensitive bog ecosystems. This process destroys habitat and releases carbon into the atmosphere. Our peat-free alternatives use coconut coir, composted bark, and other sustainable materials that provide excellent drainage and aeration without the environmental impact.
    </p>
    
    <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      We also add beneficial microorganisms to our soil blends. These helpful bacteria and fungi form symbiotic relationships with plant roots, helping them absorb nutrients more efficiently and resist disease. This means your plants will grow faster, stronger, and healthier.
    </p>
    
    <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      Fast delivery is important to us. We know you want to start using your new soil right away, so we ship all orders within 24-48 hours. Most customers receive their order within 3-5 business days, depending on location.
    </p>
  </section>

